			<abstract>The aim of the EHRI Terezín Research Guide is to create a comprehensive, innovative and easy to use guide through the dispersed
				and fragmented Terezín (Theresienstadt) archival material and to empower further research on the history of the ghetto. </abstract>
			<repository>Beit Terezin</repository>
			<repository>Terezin Memorial</repository>
			<repository>Yad Vashem</repository>
			<repository>Jewish Museum Prague</repository>
			<origination>
